[section#simd.traits
    [:en] Type traits
    [:zh_CN] 类型特征
]

[%@lib@member alignment[!simd]]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class T, class U = typename T::value_type> struct alignment { [[redoc("[=seebelow]")]] };
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] [`alignment<T, U>] has a member [`value] if and only if
[`T] is a specialization of [`basic_vec] and [`U] is a vectorizable type.
[:zh_CN] 当且仅当 [`T] 是 [`basic_vec] 的特例，且 [`U] 为可向量化类型时，
[`alignment<T, U>] 具有成员 [`value]。

[para]
[:en] If [`value] is present, the type [`alignment<T, U>] is a
[`BinaryTypeTrait] with a base characteristic of [`integral_constant<size_t, N>]
for some unspecified [`N] ([#simd.ctor], [#simd.loadstore]).
[:zh_CN] 当存在 [`value] 时，类型 [`alignment<T, U>] 是 [`BinaryTypeTrait]，它具有
某个未指明 [`N] 的 [`integral_constant<size_t, N>] 的基本特征（[#simd.ctor]，[#simd.loadstore]）。

[begin:note]
[:en] [`value] identifies the alignment restrictions on pointers used for
(converting) loads and stores for the given type [`T] on arrays of type [`U].
[:zh_CN] 对于用于在类型 [`U] 的数组上对给定类型 [`T] 进行加载和存储（转换）的指针，
[`value] 标明它的对齐限制条件。
[end:note]
[div:end]

[%@lib@member rebind[!simd]]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class T, class V> struct rebind { using type = [[redoc("[=seebelow]", "_")]]_; };
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] The member [`type] is present if and only if
[:zh_CN] 当且仅当以下情况下，存在成员 [`type]：
[list]
[item]
[:en@~] [`V] is a data-parallel type,
[:zh_CN@~] [`V] 为数据并行类型，
[item]
[:en@~] [`T] is a vectorizable type, and
[:zh_CN@~] [`V] 为可向量化类型，并且
[item]
[:en@~] [`[*deduce-abi-t]<T, V::size()>] names an ABI tag type.
[:zh_CN@~] [`[*deduce-abi-t]<T, V::size()>] 指名一个 ABI 标签类型。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] If [`V] is a specialization of [`basic_vec], let [`Abi1] denote
an ABI tag such that [`basic_vec<T, Abi1>::size()] equals [`V::size()].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`V] 是 [`basic_vec] 的特例，令 [`Abi1] 代表使得
[`basic_vec<T, Abi1>::size()] 等于 [`V::size()] 的 ABI 标签。

[:en] If [`V] is a specialization of [`basic_mask], let [`Abi1] denote an
ABI tag such that [`basic_mask<sizeof(T), Abi1>::size()] equals [`V::size()].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`V] 是 [`basic_mask] 的特例，令 [`Abi1] 代表使得
[`basic_mask<sizeof(T), Abi1>::size()] 等于 [`V::size()] 的 ABI 标签。

[para]
[:en] Where present, the member typedef [`type] names [`basic_vec<T, Abi1>]
if [`V] is a specialization of [`basic_vec] or [`basic_mask<sizeof(T), Abi1>]
if [`V] is a specialization of [`basic_mask].
[:zh_CN] 如果存在，那么成员 typedef [`type] 当 [`V] 为 [`basic_vec] 的特例时指名
[`basic_vec<T, Abi1>]，或当 [`V] 为 [`basic_mask] 的特例时指名 [`basic_mask<sizeof(T), Abi1>]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member resize[!simd]]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<[[redoc("*>")]]simd-size-type N, class V> struct resize { using type = [[redoc("[=seebelow]", "_")]]_; };
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] Let [`Abi1] denote an ABI tag
[:zh_CN] 令 [`Abi1] 代表一个 ABI 标签：
[list]
[item]
[:en@~] such that [`[*simd-size-v]<typename V::value_type, Abi1>] equals [`N]
if [`V] is a specialization of [`basic_vec],
[:zh_CN@~] 使得当 [`V] 为 [`basic_vec] 的特例时
[`[*simd-size-v]<typename V::value_type, Abi1>] 等于 [`N]，
[item]
[:en@~] otherwise such that [`[*mask-size-v]<[*mask-element-size]<V>, Abi1>]
equals [`N] if [`V] is a specialization of [`basic_mask].
[:zh_CN@~] 否则，使得当 [`V] 为 [`basic_mask] 的特例时
[`[*mask-size-v]<[*mask-element-size]<V>, Abi1>] 等于 [`N]。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] The member [`type] is present if and only if
[:zh_CN] 当且仅当以下情况下，存在成员 [`type]：
[list]
[item]
[:en@~] [`V] is a data-parallel type, and
[:zh_CN@~] [`V] 为数据并行类型，并且
[item]
[:en@~] there exists at least one ABI tag that satisfies the above constraints for [`Abi1].
[:zh_CN@~] 存在至少一个 ABI 标签满足上述针对 [`Abi1] 的约束。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] Where present, the member typedef [`type] names
[`basic_vec<typename V::value_type, Abi1, Abi1>]
if [`V] is a specialization of [`basic_vec], or
[`basic_mask<[*mask-element-size]<V>, Abi1>]
if [`V] is a specialization of [`basic_mask].
[:zh_CN] 如果存在，那么成员 typedef [`type] 当 [`V] 为 [`basic_vec] 的特例时指名
[`basic_vec<typename V::value_type, Abi1, Abi1>]，或当 [`V] 为 [`basic_mask]
的特例时指名 [`basic_mask<[*mask-element-size]<V>, Abi1>]。
[div:end]
